title: Zach Nunn Defeats Cindy Axne to Win Iowa House Seat
description: Cindy Axne was one of seven House Democrats to carry a Trump district in 2020, but could not hold off Zach Nunn, a state senator and Air Force veteran.
dc:creator: Maggie Astor
media:credit: Bryon Houlgrave/The Des Moines Register, via Associated Press
